HEADWORD: Expetible
<hw>Ex*pet"ible</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.,
<ets>expetibilis</ets>, fr. <ets>expetere</ets> to wish for;
<ets>ex</ets> out + <ets>petere</ets> to seek.]</ety> <def>Worthy of
being wished for; desirable.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>
<rj><au>Puller.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Expiable</ent>⟦br⟧
